
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "RenewableEnergy";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="content-container p-4 bg-white shadow rounded">
        <h1 class="text-center text-success">Renewable Energy in Agriculture</h1>

        <p>
            Using renewable energy will assist agricultural operations by powering water pumps and irrigation systems.
            These energy sources are naturally replenished and have a low environmental impact. Renewable energy contributes
            significantly to environmental sustainability, offering various benefits such as:
        </p>

        <ul class="custom-list">
            <li>✅ Reduced emissions</li>
            <li>✅ Improved air quality</li>
            <li>✅ Sustainable development</li>
            <li>✅ Power reliability</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
            South Africa is actively investing in renewable energy, benefiting from abundant wind in coastal areas and sunshine
            in the western regions. Our goal is to contribute to renewable electricity within the agricultural sector, positively
            impacting the environment.
        </p>

        <p>
            Recent government announcements have also allowed small-scale embedded generation, enabling industry players to generate
            electricity for their own consumption. This marks a significant step forward in achieving energy security and sustainability.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div id="energyCarousel" class="carousel slide mt-4" data-bs-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-indicators">
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#energyCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#energyCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="1"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#energyCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="2"></button>
        </div>

        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="~/Content/Images/Picture6.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Solar and Wind Energy">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="~/Content/Images/Picture5.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Solar Panels in Agriculture">
            </div>
            
        </div>

        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#energyCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#energyCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon"></span>
        </button>
    </div>
</div>

@section scripts {
    <script>
        $(document).ready(function () {
            $('#energyCarousel').carousel();
        });
    </script>
}

<style>
    .content-container {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: white;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .custom-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
    }

        .custom-list li {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #0275d8;
            padding: 5px 0;
        }

    .carousel-item img {
        height: 400px;
        object-fit: cover;
    }
</style>

